* Steve Bracks AC, 44th Premier of Victoria and former MP for Williamstown
* Bill Deller OAM, former Australian rules football umpire and director
* Tony Dodemaide, cricketer and administrator
* Richard Greaves, author and prospector
* Richard Green, golfer and racing driver
* Andy Griffiths, author
* Lachlan Hunter, AFL player
* Brad Johnson, Western Bulldogs captain
* Molly Jovic, Netballer 
* Beatrice Kerr, swimmer and diver was born in Williamstown in 1887
* Shaun Micallef, comedian and television presenter
* Wade Noonan, politician and member for Williamstown
* Mark Philippoussis, tennis player
* Rohan Smith, Western Bulldogs footballer
* Mark Viduka, Soccer Player, former Socceroos Captain
* Scott West, Western Bulldogs footballer
* Ralph Willis AO, former Member of the Federal Parliament, former Treasurer of Australia, and former Federal Member for Gellibrand

